<P>THE ROAD TO RUIN: A COMEDY.</P>
<P>AS ACTED AT THE <HI>LONDON and DUBLIN THEATRES.</HI></P>
<P>DUBLIN; Printed for J. BRA<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="2 letters">, Crow-Street, 1792.</P>
