<PB N="58" REF="57">
what of that? Why, man, the ble&s;&s;ed &s;u<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"> him&s;elf is &s;ometimes under a cloud! Wait but till to|morrow</Q>&mdash;Where is this wine?&mdash; <STAGE>[Fills the rummers]</STAGE> Come, drink, and wa&s;h away grief! 'Sblood, never look fro&s;ty and a&s;kaunce, man, but drink, drink, drink!</P>
