<P>Well&punc; well! Ha&punc; ha, ha! Tol lol&mdash;I'll bring him relief&mdash;Comfort him, a&s;&s;ure him of it!&mdash;Ay, hear me heaven and&mdash;! To-night it is too late, but to-morrow all &s;hall be well!&mdash;Excellent well!</P>
