<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sul</SPEAKER>
<P>Humph,</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Dorn.</SPEAKER>
<P>My &s;on Harry&mdash; <STAGE>[He&s;itating]</STAGE> You are a very good man, Mr Sulky; a compa&s;&s;ionate man, though you don't look &s;o,</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sul.</SPEAKER>
